if you want to stop container docker:
sudo docker stop <container name>

Docker command:
sudo docker run --name badkan -p 8010:8010 --rm -itd erelsgl/badkan bash

if get : < Got permission denied while trying to connect to the Docker daemon socket at unix:///var/run/docker.sock: Get http://%2Fvar%2Frun%2Fdocker.sock/v1.39/containers/badkan/json: dial unix /var/run/docker.sock: connect: permission denied

run 
    sudo usermod -a -G docker $USER

run the docker server:

sudo docker exec badkan bash -c "cd /www; python3 -u -m http.server 8010"

